highlights.text: “彩り七味” by GADORO is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Japan, up 16 spots at #80.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Japan. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #2.
“BON” by Number_i has been on Viral Songs Japan the longest, at 439 days straight.
“Shinpai Muyou” by Yuki Chiba and VALORANT is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Japan at #93.
